title: Bloomberg Markets: Spain's Rajoy Fires Catalan Leader
itunes:title: Bloomberg Markets: Spain's Rajoy Fires Catalan Leader
description:
Bloomberg Markets with Carol Massar and Cory Johnson.\u0010\u0010GUEST:\u0010Maria Tadeo\u0010Bloomberg New Reporter \u0010\u0010Mark Grant\u0010Chief Strategist\u0010Hilltop Securities \u0010Discussing Spanish Prime Minister Mariano Rajoy dismissing the Catalan regional government and dissolved its parliament, calling a regional election for Dec. 21, as he sought to restore control of the rebel region.
